{{Expand language|otherarticle=Alextime|date=May 2018|langcode=ru|topic=}} {{Infobox person | name = Alextime | birth_name = Aleksei Viktorovich Makeev | birth_date = {{birth date and age|1974|08|22|df=yes}} | birth_place = [[Elektrostal]], [[Moscow Oblast]], [[Russia]] | residence = [[Cancún]], [[Mexico]] | nationality = Russian | other_names = Alextime | citizenship = [[Russia]] | height = | weight = | occupation = YouTube-personality, blogger, businessman <small>(formerly)</small> | years_active = 2012–2017 (May 20) | notable_works = Aquaworld <small>(2003–2010)</small> | net_worth = 37,000,000₽ <small>(data for 2000)</small> | movement = [[Nazism]] | criminal_charge = accused of murdering a Mexican | criminal_status = in custody during the investigation | mother = Emma Nikolaevna Makeeva <small>(born 1932)</small> | father = Viktor Yakovlevich Makeev <small>(1930—2014)</small> }}
'''Aleksei Viktorovich Makeev''' ({{Lang-ru|Алексей Викторович Макеев}}; born 22 August 1974), better known as '''Alextime''' is a Russian [[List of YouTubers|YouTube-personality]] (formerly), now in custody due to suspicion of murder.
He became famous for his [[Video clip|videos]], in which he openly showed his extreme intolerance towards other people on [[Racism|ethnic grounds]] and not only, and in Mexico in 2017 an attempt was made to [[lynching|lynch]] him.
At the moment he is in the detention center of the city of [[Cancun|Cancún]] on suspicion of murder during an attempt to lynch him.
== Biography == {{Empty section|date=June 2018}}
== Unsuccessful attempt to lynch Aleksei by Mexicans == Aleksei Makeev is known for his disdainful attitude towards other people. He believes that those around him are just looking for ways to “how to piss him off”. In [[Mexico]], however, his suspicions were reinforced by his belonging to [[Russia]]. Thus, his Mexican video blog has acquired a racist character: in most of his videos one can hear discriminatory remarks about the people of Mexico because of his suspicions of discrimination of his personality.
Mexicans didn't accept this attitude to themselves, so they decided to hold a blogger over [[lynching]].<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://360tv.ru/news/tekst/kto-takoj-aleksej-makeev-i-pochemu-meksikancy-zahoteli-ego-ubit-112124/|title=Кто такой Алексей Макеев и почему мексиканцы захотели его убить|last=|first=|date=|work=Телеканал 360°|access-date=2018-05-02|language=ru}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.5-tv.ru/news/128947/|title=Скандально известного видеоблогера-дауншифтера Алексея Макеева, возможно, жестоко избили в Мексике|last=|first=|date=|work=Пятый канал|access-date=2018-05-02|language=ru}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://russian.rt.com/world/article/391646-kankun-rossiyanin-izbieniye-povedeniye|title=Мексиканская вендетта: в Канкуне россиянина избили из-за неадекватного поведения|last=|first=|date=|work=[[RT (TV network)|RT]]|access-date=2018-05-02|language=ru-RU}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|author=|first=|date=|year=|origyear=|title=Кто такой Алексей Макеев, которого в Мексике побила толпа местных жителей?|url=http://www.aif.ru/dontknows/actual/kto_takoy_aleksey_makeev_kotorogo_v_meksike_pobila_tolpa_mestnyh_zhiteley|format=|journal=Аргументы и факты|type=|series=|language=ru-RU|edition=|location=|publisher=|volume=|issue=|page=|pages=|at=|arxiv=|bibcode=|doi=|isbn=|issn=|pmid=|archiveurl=|archivedate=|quote=|ref=|via=|editor=|agency=|number=}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://inosmi.ru/social/20170522/239406520.html|title=Мексиканская толпа линчевала русского "нациста" в Канкуне|last=|first=|date=2017-05-22|work=ИноСМИ.ру|access-date=2018-05-02|language=ru}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://ren.tv/novosti/2017-05-21/mat-rossiyskogo-blogera-nacista-izbitogo-do-polusmerti-v-meksike-dur-v-internete|title=Мать российского блогера-нациста, избитого до полусмерти в Мексике: Дурь в интернете - вот и все его преступление|last=|first=|date=2017-05-21|work=РЕН ТВ|access-date=2018-05-02|language=ru-RU}}</ref> So, on '''May 20, 2017''' a large number of people gathered near the house where Alextime rented his apartment. For some time the crowd didn't attempt to break through, confining itself to verbal skirmishes and throwing stones at the windows. The police also came to the scene, but later they left. The point of boiling was the moment when one of the Mexicans climbed onto the [[terrace (building)|terrace]] and tried to provoke the blogger, and he in turn, for self-defense, caused several knife strikes, in connection with which the man died on the spot.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://ren.tv/novosti/2017-05-21/ubiystvo-meksikanca-rossiyskim-blogerom-zapechatleno-na-video-18|title=Убийство мексиканца российским блогером запечатлено на видео (18+)|last=|first=|date=2017-05-21|work=РЕН ТВ|access-date=2018-05-02|language=ru-RU}}</ref> After that, the crowd burst into Makeev's house and began brutally beating him. Later, the police arrived at the scene, stopping the mob law over Makeev, in connection with which he survived. Aleksei received a [[Traumatic brain injury|craniocerebral injury]] and was paralyzed, the doctors brought him into a state of [[artificial coma]].
After the incident, Makeev was prosecuted for his injuries, which led to the death of a nineteen-year-old Mexican. At the moment, an investigation is underway, Makeev is in the detention center of [[Cancún]].<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://lenta.ru/news/2017/06/03/odinochka/|title=Россиянин Макеев помещен в одиночную камеру в мексиканской тюрьме|last=|first=|date=|work=[[Lenta.ru]]|access-date=2018-05-02|language=ru-RU}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://ren.tv/novosti/2017-05-30/rossiyaninu-makeevu-predyavili-obvinenie-v-ubiystve-v-meksike|title=Россиянину Макееву предъявили обвинение в убийстве в Мексике|last=|first=|date=2017-05-30|work=РЕН ТВ|access-date=2018-05-02|language=ru-RU}}</ref>
